snippet.textDisplay:
I'm French and confined in my home with the love of my life and our big dog in very lucky conditions (big house with a garden, etc).. Our 4 adult kids (youngest is 18) are safe and isolated apart from us (TG!! we love them but they are driving us crazy after a couple of hours !!! :D ) and at their "home" (one of our daughters is isolated in South NZ in her van where she lives happily !!).

I don't know much about American shows, including The Office because we never wanted tv at home to preserve our family life. So I only know you and Steve through your guys' movies and I love you guys so much. So a BIG THANK YOU for doing this because you're not only entertaining America but also the rest of the English-speaking world !! If you need a local correspondant in Paris' area (I'm not that rich to live inside Paris, don't push it !! :D) feel free to let me know !

THANK YOU again and hope the laughters and fun moments helps very much those who need them. Take you all great care of yourseves. Cécile.
